titleInfo.title: Million Dollar Health and Gymnasium Underway at Tennessee Agricultural and Industrial State College

mods.abstract: Pictured are Dr. Walter S. Davis, President of Tennessee State College, Calvin McKissack of the Firm McKissack and McKissack Architect, Benson Dutton, Head of Engineering and Industrial Education, a Representative of the Harlan Construction Company, Henry A. Kean, Head Football Coach, Another Representative of the Harlan Company, A. V. Boswell, Head of Math Department and Earnest Davis a Graduate of the College. All of These People Look at Plans as Actual Work on the Gymnasium Begins.
